Class Converter

  • java.lang.Object
    • logic.Converter

  • public class Converter
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class providing methods for converting BusinessPartner to OpenZGeschaeftspartner and vice versa, converting Hipergate Group to BusinessPartnerGroup and converting BusinessPartnerGroup to OpenZBusinessPartnerGroup.
    Author:
    HAWAI
